article_title: Howell crash closed left lane of I-195
article_text:
. (Photo: WEBART)

HOWELL–Authorities are responding to a crash Tuesday morning on I-195, traffic reports say.

The crash occurred around 8:20 a.m. on I-195 westbound near Exit 31, according to the state's traffic service, 511nj.org. The left lane was closed, causing a 10 to 15 minute delay, but it has since been cleared.

This is a breaking news story. Check back with APP.com for updates.

Steph Solis: 732-643-4043; ssolis@gannettnj.com
